Package com.example.as1

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Background
    A Background class that holds a background to be used in the PlayView.
    Block
    Block class that holds a block and all of its possible attributes.
    Character
    Contains all information about a character's location difficulty appearance name
    CharCreationActivity
    Screen for creating a character
    CharSelActivity
    User is prompted to select a character to play the game with.
    FriendListActivity
    UI activity that pulls in a list of the current user's friends to show on the screen.
    FriendsActivity
    UI Activity that allows the current user to add friends via an EditText object.
    LoginActivity
    User is prompted to log in to use the core features of the app
    MainActivity
    A precursor to the app, basically a title screen
    MenuActivity
    The main menu of the game
    PlayActivity
    Activity that holds the "PlayView" which is basically the game to be run.
    PlayView
    The class that runs the logic of the game and facilitates rendering.
    RegisterActivity
    The screen for user registration to play the game
    SettingsActivity
    The screen for customizable settings within the menu
    World
    A World class that holds the map, player info and world info.
    WorldCreationActivity
    Screen for creating a world
    WorldSelActivity
    Screen for selecting a world to play on
